    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's finally time for it to find a new home. This car is practically flawless\u2014inside and out, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied it since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and the paint is still glowing. If you're looking for something that's been truly loved and is in pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
