    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained VANOS system and a fully reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary kinematic concerns. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox provides surgical shift precision, sending power through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of clear coat failure or panel misalignment, while the undercarriage remains free of any oxidation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car for those who demand mechanical purity.",
